PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 39 - which (a) DECLARES the severe 1999 spring run-off and flooding in BRITISH COLUMBIA to be of concern to the federal government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.

precis:
Enactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 39 -
which (a) DECLARES the severe 1999 spring run-off and flooding in BRITISH
COLUMBIA to be of concern to the federal government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the
provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.
